race.description: Book For Melb Cup Raceday Tue 4th Nov Mdn Hcp
race.comment: SHE'S GOT LYRICS (1) has switched from the premier Brisbane stable and has been freshened. She was narrowly beaten at Doomben two back over this distance and that's good form for this. The betting will be key. GRUMPYWANTSATISSUE (2) resumed over 1300m at Rockhampton and looked a run short beaten 2L. Presents fitter and is suited over the longer trip. Gets his chance. SUPEEDO GONZALES (5) mixes the form but went well at Townsville two back and that would see him in the finish. Has a low gate and should enjoy a soft run. MAHTIKKAINSTINCT (6) is lightly raced and on the improve. Has the rail and include in the trifectas at least.
